1604307600.title: Early Start
1604307600.descr: Early Start is a hard news morning television show on CNN anchored by Christine Romans and Laura Jarrett, aired weekdays. Keep up with the latest news and top stories of the day, stay tuned for all important events on the global arena.

1604311200.title: New Day
1604311200.descr: Alisyn Camerota and John Berman report the latest news and top stories.

1604325600.title: CNN Newsroom
1604325600.descr: CNN Newroom provides the most up to date news as it breaks and is the longest running show on the channel, airing twice a day Monday to Friday and throughout the day over the weekends. CNN was founding in 1980 by American media proprietor Ted Turner as a 24 hour cable news channel and has since won multiple media awards.

1604347200.title: The Lead with Jake Tapper
1604347200.descr: Current affairs programme hosted by the journalist and author, Jake Tapper. Jake Tapper is the chief Washington correspondent for CNN and he will share his knowledge and insight into politics as well as covering a variety of other topics. This programme discusses a range of stories from topical events including national news, economics/finance, sports, health, technology and world affairs.

1604354400.title: The Situation Room
1604354400.descr: Wolf Blitzer is in the command center for breaking news, politics and extraordinary reports from around the world.

1604361600.title: Erin Burnett OutFront
1604361600.descr: Hosted by Erin Burnett, OutFront is an hour-long news programme examining the latest stories from the US and further afield. The show features insightful opinions from informed guests, leaving no stone unturned.

1604365200.title: Anderson Cooper 360
1604365200.descr: Anderson Cooper delves into the day's news, looking beyond the broadcast to give his take, prompting us to re-think what we hear in the headlines. Cooper has covered major, international stories like the aftermath of Hurricane Katrina on the Gulf Coast, the catastrophic BP oil spill and the 2010 earthquake in Haiti, which saw the whole world fall silent.

1604368800.title: Cuomo Prime Time
1604368800.descr: Chris Cuomo gets after it with newsmakers in Washington and around the world.

1604372400.title: CNN Tonight with Don Lemon
1604372400.descr: Late-night news programme brought to you by Don Lemon and the news team at CNN. Bringing you comprehensive coverage of news from the USA and around the world. This hour-long broadcast features analysis, opinion and insight on the day's top stories. Don Lemon is an award-winning American television journalist who joined CNN in 2006.
